cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it presents a training system for defending neural networks. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it deals with deep residual networks and their defense. Additionally, it may be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as it presents a provable defense method. Finally, it may also be classified under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it introduces a flexible domain-specific language for describing training objectives.
